			<div class="content" id="post-content-2220710">
									

<p>This starts out alright, and then it gets really, <em>really</em> good. The new concepts in particular are great, and made even better by the punchy, entertaining explanations. And about 2/3 through it <em>seriously</em> turns into a head trip, and that's impressive given how inured I am to these ideas.</p>
<p>Marvelously done. +1</p>

