<blockquote>
<p>(number unknown): a &quot;contagious murder&quot;. This is the death of SCP researcher Bart Hughes. He is dead, but anybody who learns exactly how he died immediately dies by precisely the same method. So, obviously the cause of death cannot be explicitly documented. In fact, the entire series of deaths (who knows how many!) has to be strenuously quarantined to prevent it from spreading.</p>
</blockquote>
